attributes.title: Stoner Munchies Mindf*ck - Part 2
attributes.caption: Things start getting weird at the local mall for The Class of 198X as mysterious invaders make their presence known.
attributes.description: Things start getting weird at the local mall for The Class of 198X as mysterious invaders make their presence known. Also four teenagers humiliate a mall cop and Trevor learns about diet soda.

attributes.title: VINTAGE TEENAGE VIOLENCE - Part 3

attributes.title: SECRET SLAVES OF THE SPIDER - Part 6
attributes.caption: On an all new CLASS OF 198X, the gang confronts the hideous alien spider from last week's cliffhanger and Amanda does some of her best work putting the group in danger.

attributes.title: DANCE BATTLE OF DINOSAUR JUNGLE -  Part  7
attributes.caption: On a very special CLASS OF 198X, we ask: how do you know if the party is too drunk?
attributes.description: On a very special CLASS OF 198X, we ask: how do you know if the party is too drunk? This week has got it all: dance battles, giant jungle creatures, dramatic real life enactments with very large weapons, sex scenes and ILLEGAL DRUGS. We packed it all in before next week's big finale, so bear with our blood alcohol level and join the party!

attributes.title: FINAL EXAM FEVER DREAMS - Part 8
attributes.caption: For the Class of 198X, it all comes down to this, THE FINAL BATTLE.
attributes.description: For the Class of 198X, it all comes down to this, THE FINAL BATTLE. Bear witness to our two-hour season finale as the teens take on the alien invader leadership and push their friendship to the limits of survival. Who will step up to become a hero and who will stay a huge piece of shit? Find out the fates of Amanda, Sam, Mike, Hannah, Steve and the kobolds right now on the CLASS OF 198X.
